                    "name": "Drain Life",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "When the devourer damages a living creature with its claw Strike, the devourer gains 10 temporary Hit Points and the creature must succeed at a DC 24 Fortitude save or become <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">drained 1</a>. Further damage dealt by the devourer increases the condition value by 1 on a failed save, to a maximum of drained 4.",
